m1 <- glmer(n_tweets_by_user_in_state ~ 1 + 
              
              scale(time_of_account)+

              scale(voices) +

              scale(c_ideology) +
              scale(g_ideology) +

              scale(three_year_average_of_state_poverty_rates_2015_2017) +
              scale(pct_students_frpl) +
